T*
(When placed in a uniform electric field E, equal and opposite forces act on the two) Tj
T*
(charges and form a couple.) Tj
T*
(Magnitude of torque: tau = p*E*sin\(theta\)) Tj
T*
(where theta is the angle between dipole moment and electric field.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The torque tends to align the dipole in the direction of the electric field.) Tj
T*
() Tj
